snippet.title: Installation 01 Trailer Spot
snippet.description:
This video represents an older era of Installation 01, please check in with our socials below for recent updates.

Installation 01 is a free, fan-made Halo game by a team of passionate fans from around the globe. Our goal is bring a unique classic Halo multiplayer experience to PC.

Visit our website to check in on our progress! https://installation01.org

Or check out our commits page to our internal progress in real time! https://installation.org/commits

======================================

https://twitter.com/Installation01
https://www.instagram.com/installation_01/
https://www.twitch.tv/installation01

======================================
